ent-CMHyperSleepChamber-name = hypersleep chamber
ent-CMHyperSleepChamber-desc = A large automated capsule with LED displays intended to put anyone inside into 'hypersleep', a form of non-cryogenic statis used on most ships, linked to a long-term hypersleep bay on a lower level.

